title: Giac Duyen
description: Long-time operating vegetarian restaurant, re-opened at this location a couple door down from previous location at 22 Nguyen Huy Tu. Small, simple place with extensive menu in English. Some English spoken. A few pictures posted on the walls. Offers traditional variety of soups, rice and noodle dishes, with some mock meats along with the vegetables. No added MSG.
streetAddress: 16 Nguyen Huy Tu, Da Kao, District 1
